name: Anything and Everything
description:
AnE v5 is out,

Featuring a semi-realistic art style, the newest edition in my Anything and Everything series is here!


Keeping with the style of my previous versions, this one has been remixed from the bottom up - removing some subpar models and adding some new ones! Just don't ask what, because I didn't write it down. I tried to include a wide variety of example pics, many of them do use a LoRA for their gen.
